Estimation & Costs

Use 2D drawings and 3D models to create accurate budgets, BOQs, BOMs, Material Schedules and Estimates.

Takeoff quantities using various measurement tools

  • Measure length, width, height, drop length, area, perimeter, volume, counts, etc. at multiple units of measurement
  • Link measurements directly with Cost Databases such as DSR, PAR to create code-compliant estimates
  • Created for estimators and surveyors - adaptable and easy to learn

An enhanced BIM based 3D Estimation tool

  • Advanced filters to manage data and create views for relevant data - teams view only information which is relevant to them
  • Automated quantity takeoff with ability to filter, segregate, sort and organise information rapidly.
  • An integrated approach towards estimation ensures you can use 3D models, 2D drawings and manual measurements to increase accuracy and reduce redundant errors

Manage multiple heirarchical Cost Databases with ease

  • Measure length, width, height, drop length, area, perimeter, volume, counts, etc. at multiple units of measurement
  • Link measurements directly with Cost Databases such as DSR, PAR to create code-compliant estimates
  • Created for estimators and surveyors - adaptable and easy to learn
